codex
I confirmed the concrete gap: when `compiled_primary_family` is `frame` but adaptive logits rank a different top family, the compiler currently only emits the `frame -> top_family` explicit pair and can miss `frame -> conditional_normative` / `frame -> deontic` even with low margins. I’m patching that mismatch path to evaluate those frame policy targets too, then adding a regression test that would fail on current code.
